creator: St. Teresa of Avila
description:
LibriVox recording of The Relations of Saint Teresa of Avila by St. Teresa of Avila. (Translated by David Lewis.)
Read in English by Ann Boulais

The Relations (in Spanish Relaciones) is an extention of St Teresa's Autobiography. In The Relations she tells of her inner and outer experiences in the form of letters. - Summary by Ann Boulais

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
